{"tid":1744921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想寫個黃色經濟圈既APP，希望大家可以比啲意見","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:42:49.000Z","uid":28410,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"1825d15496051a95e89bd7ebef33247a10161aa9","tid":1744921,"uid":28410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:34:53.000Z","msg":"(幫朋友開POST, 佢冇AC)<br />\n<br />\n小弟朋友係一位IT9，見到而家網上大部份APP/website 都係純資訊型，而且好多時資源都傾斜左一邊<br />\n所以希望想寫多隻APP出黎幫助個運動，如果可行，佢會請大假全職寫出黎<br />\n<br />\n個APP主要目的有兩個:  <br />\n1. 資源更有效分配。show 邊啲黃店比人懲罰得最多，邊啲冇乜人理。大家見到冇乜人理果啲可以盡量去幫手<br />\n2. 統計個人黃藍分數。show自己消費習慣有幾黃，提醒番自己要去幫襯多啲。<br />\n<br />\n問題係要用家每日輸入番自己去過邊間餐廳(唔係食既都得)，洗過幾多錢(約數就得)，咁先會計到數。  咁既話大家仲會唔會用?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外最後都希望隻APP唔只香港人會用, 仲吸引到遊客都去用.  界面可能會用英文寫. 仲有冇其他方向可以做到呢樣野??<br />\n<br />\n或者有冇其他新方向, 有需要既功能但而家仲係缺乏, 未有人做都可以提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef38b81970d8885b1c06dd4a066583e4c577e92f","tid":1744921,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8FC98h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8FC98h.png&h=6d8e3d3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5f315734cf371be86725d9a8ede504da7a4a560","tid":1744921,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"會用，推"},{"pid":"ac6bcffa34cd5dc34f54a815a0e8ad63fd530c06","tid":1744921,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"[行動post-行動代號21000730]星期六晚9點前返屋企訓教，星期日730等票站開門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1738555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1738555</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":