 而去分類黃藍?"},{"pid":"153de58416dfa61ebd34e8d62d888bb6dd62e4cb","tid":1744921,"uid":28410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6348b496bc1ad6e017183d84d48c7fcabe951b9f","tid":1744921,"uid":66970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a6b35524ab971ec1adee30c32845cde368dcdc65","tid":1744921,"uid":66970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"可以approach下現有嘅平台啲admin喎<br />\n睇下有無機會合作/share database，慳返啲時間同人力呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"同埋講餐廳而家有和理eat，相信都幾多人覺得好用<br />\n可以考慮下專做非餐廳嘅商户呀<br />\n明白巴打想加入新功能，但我覺得比起評分等嘅功能，其實有個apps方便大家搵到間舖更重要，之後再發展都得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"評分其實係次要     主要係想資源平均啲分配<br />\n而家好似一係就全部人集中去某幾間   一係就完全冇人去搞到就執先搵人去<br />\n希望優先改善呢個情況"},{"pid":"bfe0d83782f5c421130d5bf13ea13257061cc207","tid":1744921,"uid":66970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13cf371a4af3b89d443e03f961992a109b4ad291","tid":1744921,"uid":28410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de366f66dc5c671bb0af428969333de63efb037e","tid":1744921,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"希望做返個分類 <br />\n唔好剩係得餐廳<br />\n<br />\n希望個ui唔會好疾<br />\n或者可以剩係redirect去google map<br />\n唔駛自己執個map入app會唔會無咁疾？<br />\n<br />\n希望啲料係真確性高<br />\n 加返個review可以俾comment老闆<br />\n又可以等多啲人知道個「黃度」<br />\n<br />\n加油呀 so far都未有一個覺得好好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n資料係真確性呢度, 想問下而家有冇平台係比人報料間店曾經做過啲咩, 而去分類黃藍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"有，黃藍商店地圖<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScK0QXdL6toFFDS716UZ9BoSYuRSOWslJu9vIw0RetQyW0oGQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScK0QXdL6toFFDS716UZ9BoSYuRSOWslJu9vIw0RetQyW0oGQ%2Fviewform&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt81pzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=4efbd1aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScK0QXdL6toFFDS716UZ9BoSYuRSOWslJu9vIw0RetQyW0oGQ/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"b999c1117c80e88a1e239a0d28adbb869d878602","tid":1744921,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"自由市場<br />\n如果係黃，但啲野唔得一樣冇人買<br />\n<br />\n之前有人整啲平台出黎<br />\n但最大問題係，未表態既冇得睇<br />\n要成功，必定要個app變成消費指南，而黃藍係比用家既參考，分別對待係顯示既資料詳盡<br />\n例如藍店得個名同地址，未表態既有埋基本資料，黃既當然盡量詳盡介紹<br />\n先要令個app好用，廣泛，再係內容引導幫襯黃店，藍絲傻仔都可能會中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二要分類，之前有人做左啲平台成堆點係個地圖，慢慢點，點得黎我都買左食左，好用相當重要<br />\n<br />\n第三係整合，有心做不如聯合埋之前造平台既人一齊做，令個app成為主流先有用，想做既人有好多，但大家都各自渣住一啲料，分散晒其實冇用，我覺得都可以同612攞funding 做，612其實有好多錢。如果真係聯合到，你地諗個辦法攞個民意授權，例如搞網上公投等等<br />\n<br />\n個人睇法，勇武抗爭唔可以打十年八載，我地要打經戰，希望香港it人團結爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81bfea44ec887f193ab088151ba160b3caa0e1e3","tid":1744921,"uid":13330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以設計一個獎勵系統<br />\n推動學生強身健體<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eddb018459c6cfcee0e31ca639ee167101597f","tid":1744921,"uid":66862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好再寫新app<br />\n資訊太散亂...<br />\n與其係咁, 不如同現有app, 和你eat 合作"},{"pid":"845abe085d7fde914bc8840ca0e994cba0b215b5","tid":1744921,"uid":158067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"個陣時去台灣搵食覺得好好用。 又簡單又方便。<br />\n寫晒咁多行業我驚有排load<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKpMi9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKpMi9e.jpg&h=7667ea13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSkomnA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%